{"_id":"4iqvbNXdL5YElkgt","name":"The Scales Of Life And Death","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When <strong>someone takes their last breath</strong> in your presence, they take +1 to the roll.</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"901uEUL4f8so6zAL","name":"Deity","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>You serve and worship some deity or power which grants you spells. Give your god a name and choose your deity’s domain:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Healing and Restoration</li>\n<li>Bloody Conquest</li>\n<li>Civilization</li>\n<li>Knowledge and Hidden Things</li>\n<li>The Downtrodden and Forgotten</li>\n<li>What Lies Beneath</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Choose one precept of your religion:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>It preaches the sanctity of suffering, add <strong>Petition: Suffering</strong></li>\n<li>It’s clutish and insular, add <strong>Petition: Gaining Secrets</strong></li>\n<li>It Observes important sacrificial rites, add <strong>Petition: Offering</strong></li>\n<li>It believes in trial by combat, add Petition: <strong>Personal Victory</strong></li>\n</ul>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"BPHGI45yiqOFGSQb","name":"Invigorate","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>heal someone</strong> they take +2 forward to their damage.</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"Dp4N2vTW1n8WfZ7S","name":"Cast A Spell","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>unleash a spell granted by your deity</strong>, roll+WIS. • On a 10+ the the spell is successfully cast and your deity does not revoke the spell, so you may cast it again.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>On a 7-9 the spell is cast, but choose one:</li>\n<li>You draw unwelcome attention or put yourself in a spot. The GM will tell you how.</li>\n<li>Your casting distances you from your deity; take -1 ongoing to cast a spell until the next time you commune.</li>\n<li>After it is cast, the spell is revoked by your deity. You cannot cast the spell again until you commune and have it granted to you.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note that maintaining spells with ongoing effects will sometimes cause a penalty to your roll to cast a spell.</p>","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Divine Invincibility","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>Commune </strong>you gain 2 hold and lose any hold you already had. Spend that hold when you or an ally takes damage to call on your deity, who intervenes with an appropriate manifestation (a sudden gust of wind, a lucky slip, a burst of light) and negates the damage.</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Divine Intervention","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"ErHEWqf7MpYihIYZ"}
{"_id":"FbSjts1kZ0dWNwrz","name":"Penitent","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you<strong> take damage</strong> and embrace the pain, you may take +1d4 damage (ignoring armor). If you do, take +1 forward to cast a spell.</p>\n<p>Bonus damage roll: [[/roll 1d4]]</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"name":"Devoted Healer","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you<strong> heal someone else </strong>of damage, add your level to the amount of damage healed.</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"Gsi2Ci5zPExlUIfp"}
