{"name":"Greater Empower","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you<strong> cast a spell</strong>, on a 10-11 you have the option of choosing from the 7–9 list. If you do, you may choose one of these effects as well. On a 12+ you get to choose one of these effects for free.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The spell’s effects are doubled</li>\n<li>The spell’s targets are doubled</li>\n</ul>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"Empower","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"Vf2TZaZKUFIdtmO6"}
