{"_id":"Y5eKALcZvyiK1Ecu","name":"Turn Undead","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>When you <strong>hold your holy symbol aloft and call on your deity for protection</strong>, roll+Wis. • On a 7+, so long as you continue to pray and brandish your holy symbol, no undead may come within reach of you. • On a 10+, you also momentarily daze intelligent undead and cause mindless undead to flee. Aggression breaks the effects and they are able to act as normal.</p>","rollType":"WIS","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":0,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"starting"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
