{"name":"Apotheosis","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"move","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>The first time you <strong>spend time in prayer</strong> as appropriate to your god after taking this move, choose a feature associated with your deity (rending claws, wings of sapphire feathers, an all-seeing third eye, etc.). When you emerge from prayer, you permanently gain that physical feature.</p>","rollType":"","rollMod":0,"requiresLevel":6,"requiresMove":"","moveType":"advanced"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","_id":"rOWp3xspvxCiYUW7"}
